<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，請問是哪位呢？<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我好像沒有見過你，<delay20 />
是新來的朋友嗎<tag a="110" b="0" />？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />既然在夢境裡面，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種事<delay8 />就不用太在意了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，初次見面！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很高興能見到你。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是能在這留下<delay20 />
美好的回憶就好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">哎呀，<delay8 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請問<tag a="110" b="0" />你是哪位？<delay40 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來在夢境裡<delay20 />也會遇到陌生人啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到竟然能在夢境裡見到你，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是浪漫呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">哎呀，<tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />居然能在這種地方碰到你，<delay20 />
還真是巧呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到竟然會在這裡<delay8 />遇到認識的人，
真是令人意外呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這不是<tag a="110" b="4" />嘛！<delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我問你喔，<delay8 />你不覺得這裡雖然很像我們的島，<delay20 />
但好像又有點不一樣呀？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道<delay20 />這就是傳聞中<delay8 />
夢境裡的世界嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">哎呀，<tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你好<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還是這種時候<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />應該要說「晚安」才對呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在夢境裡到底該怎麼打招呼，<delay8 />
真是讓人煩惱呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />居然能在這種地方碰到你，<delay20 />
還真是巧呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如何啊？<delay20 />
在夢境裡的<tag a="110" b="33" />上<delay8 />
散步的感覺好嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我總覺得<delay8 />身體比平常還要輕盈呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是錯覺嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。
</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />能像這樣在夢境裡跟你聊天，<delay8 />
也很令人高興呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請放輕鬆，慢慢逛吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">沒想到竟然能在這地方遇見其他人，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我有種命中注定的感覺呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">就算是夢境，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也不是任何事情都做得到喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然周遭的景色和平時不同，<delay20 />
但奇妙的是沒有一絲異樣的感覺呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這也是因為身處夢境中嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />醒來之後，<delay8 />
我們會忘記彼此在這相遇的事情嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到這，<delay8 />就覺得有點虛幻呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>